{"word":"G4520 - σαββατισμός - sabbatismós - sab-bat-is-mos' - Rest","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σαββατισμός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>sabbatismós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>sab-bat-is-mos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Rest"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"இளைப்பாறுகிற காலம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. a keeping sabbath"},{"paragraph":"2. the blessed rest from toils and troubles looked for in the age to come by the true worshippers of God and true Christians"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4521 - σάββατον - sábbaton - sab'-bat-on/4521\">G4521</a>; a &ldquo;sabbatism&rdquo;, that is, (figuratively) the <i>repose</i> of Christianity (as a type of heaven): - rest."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4520 - σαββατισμός - sabbatismós - sab-bat-is-mos'/4520\">G4520</a>, <a href=\"#/G4521 - σάββατον - sábbaton - sab'-bat-on/4521\">G4521</a>"}]}